creator: Distributor Software Solutions, Inc
descriptionHtml:
CED Greentech Connect - Your one stop solution for all your electrical needs. Rich product information, technical data and availability makes your ordering process easy. Access your account information, real-time order updates, statements and transaction history.

- Place orders or request quotes
- View order status
- Receive notifications on order updates
- View invoices and statements
- Create custom product lists
- Scan barcodes
- Upload a product photo for a quote
- View account Information
